name: VEED
public_notice: VEED had recently migrated from their old contract to a new one on BNB Smart Chain, kindly refer to this post for more information.

description.en: VEED is the ecosystem utility and governance token of VIMworld, a Smart NFT project built on VeChainThor focused on VIM collectibles. The VEED token is used for a variety of utilities within the VIMworld Ecosystem, including VIM feeding, trading, adoption, farming, rewards, governance, and more.
